        {
          "id": "b114c603-4071-48d7-8187-f88bb913c6c0",
          "name": "第五章 Linux命令",
          "createdAt": "2026-02-26T14:35:04.955Z",
          "questions": [
            {
              "id": "52c4a222-1154-4d72-a009-60f033c898ea",
              "title": "介绍下常见的Linux命令",
              "content": "文件相关：mv、mkdir、cd、ls\n\n进程相关：ps、top、netstate\n\n权限相关：chmod、chown、useradd、groupadd\n\n网络相关：netstat、ip、addr\n\n测试连通性相关：ping、telnet",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T08:53:40.705Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:41:26.944Z",
              "srs": {
                "ease": 2.5,
                "intervalDays": 0,
                "repetitions": 1,
                "dueAt": "2026-03-05T01:41:26.944Z",
                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:41:26.944Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "07a34ba5-da28-4c70-9002-0ee36f691e2b",
              "title": "ps命令展示哪些东西？",
              "content": "进程ID、父进程ID、进程所属用户\n\nCPU占用率、内存占用率、虚拟内存大小、物理内存大小\n\n终端设备、进程状态、进程启动时间、CPU累计占用时间、进程命令",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T08:55:35.257Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:42:18.924Z",
              "srs": {
                "ease": 2.5,
                "intervalDays": 0,
                "repetitions": 1,
                "dueAt": "2026-03-05T01:42:18.924Z",
                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:42:18.924Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "7d2b71ba-9477-4cb7-9ce8-07a00615d126",
              "title": "ps命令选项？",
              "content": "-a 显示所有进程，包括其他用户的进程\n-u 显示用户相关进程信息\n-e 和 -a一样\n-f 显示进程详细信息\n-l 显示完整的进程信息，包括进程IO、父进程ID、CPU占用率等\n-r 正在运行的进程\n-o 自定义输出格式",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T08:59:32.620Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:43:21.311Z",
              "srs": {
                "ease": 2.5,
                "intervalDays": 0,
                "repetitions": 1,
                "dueAt": "2026-03-05T01:43:21.311Z",
                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:43:21.311Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "48ccd679-76c7-4d41-835d-bf5475af5834",
              "title": "top命令会展示什么东西？",
              "content": "Load average平均负载：显示系统近1分钟、5分钟和15分钟内的平均负载情况\n\nTasks任务：显示当前运行、睡眠、停止和僵尸状态的进程数量\n\nCPU Usage：显示CPU总体使用率和每个CPU核心的使用率\n\nMemory usage：显示物理内存总量、已使用量、未使用量、缓冲区和缓冲区使用量\n\nSwap Usage：交换空间总量、已使用量和未使用量\n\n进程列表：包括进程的详细信息",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T09:01:58.310Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:45:00.923Z",
              "srs": {
                "ease": 2.5,
                "intervalDays": 0,
                "repetitions": 1,
                "dueAt": "2026-03-05T01:45:00.923Z",
                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:45:00.923Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "d34421c6-7d40-4500-9aa6-a417d264865d",
              "title": "怎么杀死一个进程？",
              "content": "寻找进程的PID\nps -ef | grep 进程名\n\n终止进程\nkill PID",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T09:09:39.521Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:45:27.130Z",
              "srs": {
