            {
              "id": "56176279-db8e-43d1-be09-0065043093a9",
              "title": "搜索特定名字的文件的命令是？",
              "content": "在当前目录查找：find . -name \"xxx.txt\"\n\n在整个系统查找：find / -name \"nginx.conf\"\n\n支持通配符查找",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T09:22:32.044Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:45:51.714Z",
              "srs": {
                "ease": 2.5,
                "intervalDays": 0,
                "repetitions": 1,
                "dueAt": "2026-03-05T01:45:51.714Z",
                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:45:51.714Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "5fa1300e-05eb-42c6-98ba-72e47de451a8",
              "title": "如何查看线程状态？",
              "content": "top -H 可以查看线程，top是看进程\n\nps -eT | grep 进程或线程名  # 列出系统所有进程以及其对应的所有线程的命令",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T09:22:40.344Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:46:11.811Z",
              "srs": {
                "ease": 2.5,
                "intervalDays": 0,
                "repetitions": 1,
                "dueAt": "2026-03-05T01:46:11.811Z",
                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:46:11.811Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "0cf864b6-5bd2-484c-b98d-245e79eb9337",
              "title": "如何查看网络连接情况？",
              "content": "netstat -napt\n\n可以显示服务器上的tcp连接的状态，和四元组（源ip、目的ip、源端口、目的端口）",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T09:34:36.572Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:46:28.259Z",
              "srs": {
                "ease": 2.5,
                "intervalDays": 0,
                "repetitions": 1,
                "dueAt": "2026-03-05T01:46:28.259Z",
                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:46:28.259Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "ed66938a-26fc-42bb-b58b-2e7829236cc8",
              "title": "怎么查看哪个端口被占用？",
              "content": "lsof -i :80  # 解释：lsof是list open file的意思，列出系统中所有打开的文件，-i是专门用来筛选网络相关的打开文件\n\nnetstat -napt | grep 80 # n是不解析ip和端口号，直接显示；-a是显示所有连接和监听端口；-p是显示进程名和PID；t是只看tcp协议\n",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T09:36:05.381Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:46:54.484Z",
              "srs": {
                "ease": 2.5,
                "intervalDays": 0,
                "repetitions": 1,
                "dueAt": "2026-03-05T01:46:54.484Z",
                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:46:54.484Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "1577396c-6fbb-49b8-8184-969091305dab",
              "title": "端口通不通用什么命令？",
              "content": "telnet ip 端口号\n\nnc -zv ip 端口号 # z是zero，不发送任何数据，-v是显示详细信息",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T09:46:13.086Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:47:17.790Z",
              "srs": {
                "ease": 2.5,
                "intervalDays": 0,
                "repetitions": 1,
                "dueAt": "2026-03-05T01:47:17.790Z",
                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:47:17.790Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "2b3f928c-1152-4980-9b01-bd8cbb4634af",
              "title": "top命令如何查看有多少个CPU核心？",
              "content": "执行top命令后，按数字1",
