                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:55:43.670Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "10a4940c-3cf4-4f94-aa67-94dd92f01e3f",
              "title": "git merge和git rebase有什么区别？",
              "content": "git merge合并，会保留两个分支所有提交记录，并创建一个新的合并提交来整合两个分支的修改\n\ngit rebase，将一个分支上的每个提交逐个应用到另一个分支上，按照时间进行顺序进行线性排列，会修改历史",
              "createdAt": "2026-03-01T13:08:37.957Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T01:55:46.406Z",
              "srs": {
                "ease": 2.5,
                "intervalDays": 0,
                "repetitions": 1,
                "dueAt": "2026-03-05T01:55:46.406Z",
                "lastReviewedAt": "2026-03-05T01:55:46.406Z",
                "lapses": 0,
                "lastQuality": 2,
                "state": 2
              }
